From 37b93ae6101f31577b25ac2c043a6a8453efb3db Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <quic_nandhaki@quicinc.com>
Date: Fri, 5 Jan 2024 10:04:41 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 03/14] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: Add HTT APIs for rx flow tagging

1. Set Rx flow tagging initialization parameters to firmware using HTT
command.
2. Send RX FSE cache invalidation commands to firmware on addition of
deletion of flow entries.

Signed-off-by: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <quic_nandhaki@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Nithyanantham Paramasivam <quic_nithp@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Karthikeyan Periyasamy <quic_periyasa@quicinc.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.h     |   9 ++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_htt.c | 129 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_htt.h |  97 +++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_rx.c  |  24 +++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_rx.h  |   8 ++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hal.h    |   1 +
 6 files changed, 268 insertions(+)

